H0.text: The port of Immingham is to be found on which estuary. Thames

H1.text: The port of Immingham is to be found on which estuary. Severn

H2.text: The port of Immingham is to be found on which estuary. Mersey

H3.text: The port of Immingham is to be found on which estuary. Humber

A4.text: The Port of Immingham, also known as Immingham Dock, is a major port on the east coast of England, located on the south bank of the Humber Estuary in the town of Immingham, Lincolnshire.
